msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-02-26-quarkus-3-32-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50975[#50975] - Rework graceful shutdown to be more graceful with respect to HTTP"
msgstr ""

